<page>
   <topic>table.EVAL Function</topic>
    <description>Evaluate an expression in the context of the table.</description>
   <syntax>A Eval(C expression)</syntax>
   <arguments>
     <argument>
         <name>expression</name>
         <description>An Xbasic expression.</description>
     </argument>
   </arguments>
  
   <discussion><![CDATA[
The <TBL>.EVAL() method evaluates an expression in the context of a table.
 ]]>  </discussion>
   <example><![CDATA[
dim tbl as P
tbl = table.open("customer")
? tbl.eval("firstname+lastname")
= "Mederos Michael" 
]]></example>
   
